\c 21 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 21\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Galata Mo'icha Booddee Dhi'eeffamu (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, mootiin humna ati argisiiftutti in gammada, mo'icha akka inni argatuuf gargaaruu keetiif gammachuu guddaa attamii in qabaata.
\m \bd 2\bd* Hawwa garaa isaa isaaf kenniteetta, waan inni sitti himates isa hin dhowwanne!
\m \bd 3\bd* Ati waan gaariidhaan isa eebbisuuf gara isaa dhufteetta, gonfoo warqee qullaa'aa irraa hojjetames mataa isaa irra keesseetta.
\m \bd 4\bd* Inni jiraachuudhaaf si kadhate, atis jireenya in laatteef, guyyoota jireenya isaas baraa hamma bara baraatti dheeressiteef.
\m \bd 5\bd* Mo'icha akka inni argatuuf gargaaruu keetiin ulfinni isaa guddaa ta'e; surraa fi simboos isa irra in keesse.
\m \bd 6\bd* Inni yeroo hundumaaf eebba akka ta'uuf isa in dhaabda, dhageettii gammachuu si duratti argamuudhaan dhufuunis isa in gammachiifta.  
\m \bd 7\bd* Mootichi Waaqayyoon in amanata, gaarummaan aabbaas akka inni hin mittiqne in godha.
\m \bd 8\bd* Harki kee diinota kee hundumaa bira in ga'a, harki kee mirgaas warra si jibban bira in ga'a.
\m \bd 9\bd* Yeroo ofii kee argisiiftutti gubaa akka iddoo ibiddaa isaan in goota; Waaqayyo dheekkamsa isaatiin isaan in fixa, ibiddis xaph isaan in godha.
\m \bd 10\bd* Ati dhala isaanii lafa irraa, sanyii isaaniis ilmaan namootaa keessaa in balleessita;
\m \bd 11\bd* hamaa yoo si irratti yaadan, yoo si irratti koratanis, fiixaan baafachuu hin danda'an.
\m \bd 12\bd* Atoo fuula duraan iddaa kee isaanitti in qabda, dugda duuba deebi'anii akka baqatanis in goota.
\m \bd 13\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo aangoo keetiin ka'i! Nuyi humna kee in faarfanna, mi'a garaa garaatiinis faarfannaa in dhageessifna.
\b 
